sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Client
    participant ESB as ESB Gateway
    participant StudentAffairs as Student Affairs Service (SOAP)

    Client->>ESB: GET /api/v1/student-affairs/attendance?nim=...&courseId=...
    activate ESB
    
    Note over ESB: Content Router & Translator
    ESB->>ESB: Map URL parameters to SOAP Request
    ESB->>ESB: Transform JSON/Params to XML (xml2js)
    
    ESB->>StudentAffairs: POST /soap/StudentAttendanceLegacyService (XML)
    activate StudentAffairs
    StudentAffairs-->>ESB: 200 OK (SOAP XML Response)
    deactivate StudentAffairs
    
    Note over ESB: Translate Response
    ESB->>ESB: Parse XML to JSON (xml2js)
    ESB->>ESB: Format to Standard API Envelope
    
    ESB-->>Client: 200 OK (JSON Response)
    deactivate ESB
